.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-2::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: chess, collecting, filmmaking, hiking, video-games, woodworking
City: marseilles, nizza, san-francisco, venice, berlin, edinburgh
 1. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
 5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4
 9. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
11. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
12. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to berlin##5
13. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person traveling to marseilles##1
14. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
15. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to nizza##5
16. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to nizza##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |     3      |       4       |     5      |   6    |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | filmmaking | chess         | collecting | hiking |
| City   | marseilles    | berlin      | san-francisco      | venice | nizza   | edinburgh |

