.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-3::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, iced-tea, lemonade, milk, soy-milk
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: romance, western, musical, mystery, superhero, epic
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 2. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4
 4. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
 8. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 9. the person watching musical movies is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person watching epic movies##2
10. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
11. the person watching western movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3    |    4     |    5    |    6     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | almond-milk | milk   | lemonade | fanta   | iced-tea |
| Movie-Genre   | western    | musical         | epic | superhero     | romance | mystery     |

