.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-4::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: march, may, august, june, july, november
There 6 different types of food: apricot, avocado, garlic, pear, radish, zucchini
 1. the person eating pear is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person eating pear##1
 4. the person eating avocado is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 5. the person eating radish is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
 7. the person eating avocado is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##5
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
 9. the person eating garlic is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
10. the person eating zucchini is somewhere to the left of the person eating garlic##5
11. the person who's birthday is in june is in an odd position##4
12. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
13. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |   3    |    4    |       5       |    6     |
| Birthday   | march     | may     | august  | november     | june | july |
| Food       | avocado | zucchini | garlic | apricot | pear          | radish   |

