 9. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere to the left of the person who likes mauve##5
10. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##5
11. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who likes ebony##1
12. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |       4       |    5    |       6       |
