6 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, prince, ritmeester, bluemaster, dannemann, game
 1. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 2. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
 3. the prince-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
 4. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 5. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 6. the game-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
 7. the ritmeester-smoker is between the game-smoker and the bluemaster-smoker##2
 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 9. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the prince-smoker##5
10. the prince-smoker is between the davidoff-smoker and the bluemaster-smoker##2
11. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the game-smoker##5
12. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
13. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
14. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the prince-smoker##3
