.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-9::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, swisher, blend, old-henry, alhambra, prince
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, bus, snowmobile, subway, tram, van
 1. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the left of the alhambra-smoker##5
 2. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 3. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
 5. the ritmeester-smoker is the ritmeester-smoker##1
 6. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
 7. the person driving the subway is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 8. the prince-smoker is somewhere to the right of the alhambra-smoker##5
 9. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
10. the prince-smoker is between the blend-smoker and the person driving the van##2
11. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
12. the person driving the tram is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
13. the prince-smoker is somewhere to the right of the blend-smoker##5
14. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the left of the prince-smoker##5
15. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4
16. the person driving the bike is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |    3     |     4      |    5    |   6    |
| Cigar   | old-henry | swisher | alhambra | blend     | prince | ritmeester |
| Transport     | tram  | bike      | bus      | snowmobile | subway  | van    |

