 4. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the person playing chess##5
 5. the person playing snooker is the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
 7. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 8. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
10. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
11. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
12. the person drinking lemonade is the person playing bridge##1
13. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5     |       6       |
| Beverage   | water  | tea        | sprite  | fanta     | lemonade | hot-chocolate |
| Game       | canasta | snooker | chess | whist | bridge  | mah-jongg          |

