.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-20::.
6 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, hedgehog, horse, lizard, snake
The people have 6 different jobs:  pilot, dressmaker, doctor, nurse, bartender, teacher
 1. the bartender is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 2. the teacher is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
 3. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the dressmaker##1
 4. the owner of the fish is the bartender##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 6. the dressmaker is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the dressmaker is on the left or right of the nurse##3
 8. the pilot is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
 9. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
10. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the bartender##1
11. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the teacher##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5     |   6    |
| Pet         | snake    | horse | fish   | hedgehog | ferret    | lizard |
| Job   | pilot | teacher  | bartender | doctor      | nurse | dressmaker    |

 